{
  "translationLines": [
    {
      "lineNumber": 141291,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「ん、そうか、やはりまだ動きはないか。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Hmm, I see, so there’s still no movement after all.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 141292,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　引き続き斥候を。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Continue reconnaissance."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 141293,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　予定通り第15部隊も使い索敵範囲を広げろ」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "As planned, deploy the 15th squad as well and expand the scouting range.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 141294,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「将軍、新しい情報です――」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"General, we have new information--\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 141295,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "アミトスは次々と部下から入る情報を聞き、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Amitos listened to the incoming reports from his subordinates one after another,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 141296,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "指示を出している。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "and was issuing orders."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 141297,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「すまないな、見ての通り人手不足で",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"I’m sorry, as you can see, we’re short-handed"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 141298,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　あまり相手をしてやれそうにない」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "and can’t really spare much time for anything else.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 141299,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「将軍……",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"General..."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 141300,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　お前将軍になったのか」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "You became a general?\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 141301,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「ああ、第1軍の将だ」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Yeah, I’m the commander of the First Army.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 141302,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「ふーん、で、どうしてこんなに疲弊してる」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Hmm, so why are you so exhausted?\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 141303,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「……魔軍の兵数がああ圧倒的ではな」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"...Because the demonic army’s numbers are overwhelming.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 141304,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「特にこの方面には魔人バボラが攻め込んでいる」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Especially in this area, the demon Babbora has invaded.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 141305,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「魔人バボラ。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Demon Babbora."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 141306,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　そうか、お前ら魔人と戦ったのか」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "I see, so you fought demons.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 141307,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「戦ったなどとは言えん。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"I can’t say we fought."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 141308,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　ただ魔人の来る所を予測し民を避難させただけだ」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "We only predicted where the demons would come and evacuated the people.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 141309,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「魔人が相手となると、勝つ手段――",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"When demons are the opponent, a way to win—"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 141310,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　いや……戦う手段がないからな……」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "No... there is no way to fight them...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 141311,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「なら、こんなところ放棄したらどうだ？」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Then why not just abandon a place like this?\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 141312,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「それでは町や陣地を奪われ、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"If we do that, they would take the towns and our positions,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 141313,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　いずれはヘルマン全土が奪われる」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "and eventually the whole of Helman would fall.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 141314,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「だから魔人がいなくなると、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"That’s why whenever the demons disappear,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 141315,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　すぐに突撃で陣地を奪還しているのだ」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "we immediately launch a charge to recapture the positions.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 141316,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「それでどうにか一進一退を繰り返す。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Thus, somehow we repeat a back-and-forth struggle."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 141317,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　魔人が相手となれば、この手で戦うしかない」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "When demons are the enemy, this is the only way to fight.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 141318,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「それは……",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"That is..."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 141319,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　その、とっても大変、ですよね……」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Well, very difficult, right...?\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 141320,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「ああ、陣地をいくら奪い返しても、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Yeah, no matter how many positions we retake,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 141321,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　勝つことは出来ない……",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "we cannot win..."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 141322,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　精神的にも兵が疲弊していく」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "The soldiers are also mentally exhausted.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 141323,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「だが、負けるわけにはいかない」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"But we can’t afford to lose.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 141324,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「我々が引けば無防備な市民が",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"If we retreat, defenseless citizens"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 141325,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　魔軍の攻撃にさらされるのだ」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "will be exposed to attack by the demon army.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 141326,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「相変わらず、典型的な固い軍人だな」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Still, a typical steadfast soldier, huh.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 141327,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「ラング・バウはもう少しだ。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Rang Bau is just a little further."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 141328,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　魔軍が出るかも知れないので、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Because the demon army might appear,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 141329,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　我が軍から護衛をつけてやりたいが……」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "I want to assign escorts from our army...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 141330,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「ああ、いい、いい。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Ah, no, no."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 141331,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　こっちで適当にやる」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "I’ll handle it here appropriately.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 141332,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「すまない……」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Sorry...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 141333,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「俺様が来た以上、バボラとかいう魔人も",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Now that I’ve arrived, that demon called Babbora"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 141334,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　ちょちょいのちょいで倒してやる。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "will be defeated in no time."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 141335,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　安心することだな。がははは」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "You can rest easy. Gahaha.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 141336,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「…………そうか、あれと戦うか」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"...I see, so you will fight that one.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 141337,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「この村も一度",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"This village was also"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 141338,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　バボラに攻められたことがある」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "attacked once by Babbora.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 141339,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「あん？」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Huh?\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 141340,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「敵を知り己を知れば百戦危うからず。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"If you know the enemy and know yourself, you need not fear the outcome of a hundred battles.\""
    }
  ]
}

